data.text:
LIVE Transfer Talk: Juve still in for Man United's Sancho

Juve are reportedly still keen on Jadon Sancho, despite nearing a deal for Nico Gonzalez. Transfer Talk has the latest.

ESPN

As Mbappé waits for Madrid goal, Endrick makes it look easy

Real Madrid's Kylian Mbappé will have to wait another day for his first LaLiga goal, on a day when Endrick scored on his Los Blancos debut.

Alex Kirkland

Kylian Mbappé goals will come, Real Madrid's Carlo Ancelotti says

Real Madrid coach Carlo Ancelotti said he is not concerned about Kylian Mbappé's goal scoring after the forward failed to find the net for a second LaLiga game in a row.

Alex Kirkland, Rodrigo Faez

How Arne Slot's 'very impressive' Liverpool cruised past Brentford

Luis Miguel Echegaray praises Liverpool after their 2-0 victory in Arne Slot's first Premier League game at Anfield.

Leboeuf breaks down Kylian Mbappé's goalless Bernabeu debut

Frank Leboeuf and the "ESPN FC" crew react to Real Madrid's 3-0 win over Real Valladolid and Kylian Mbappé's failure to get on the scoresheet.

'Welcome back to the NWSL!' Trinity Rodman scores for the Spirit

Trinity Rodman's shot deflects off a defender and into the net to give the Spirit a 3-0 lead.
